### MedAssist API Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### Set @token after login

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <paste_token_here>

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "medassist123"
}

### Login as doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "doctor",
  "password": "doctor123"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# BOOKS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### List all indexed books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# QUERY — RAG hybrid search
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Disease query (English, all books)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "pneumonia treatment guidelines",
  "queryType": "Disease",
  "language": "Both",
  "webSearchEnabled": false
}

### Symptoms query filtered to a specific book
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "chest pain shortness of breath",
  "queryType": "Symptoms",
  "language": "English",
  "bookIds": ["smoke-test-v1"],
  "webSearchEnabled": false
}

### Treatment query with web search fallback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "лечение на хипертония",
  "queryType": "Treatment",
  "language": "Bulgarian",
  "webSearchEnabled": true
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# DICTIONARY
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Lookup by ICD-10 code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dictionary/J18.9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lookup hypertension
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dictionary/I10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lookup type 2 diabetes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dictionary/E11
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search by name (English)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dictionary/search?q=pneumonia
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search by name (Bulgarian)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dictionary/search?q=хипертония
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# OBSERVABILITY & DOCS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Prometheus metrics (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics

### Scalar API docs (open in browser)
### {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1
